le/GitCommit_triggers_condense` (line 143)\n- `TestTransitionFromActive/GitCommit_condenses_immediately` (line 199)\n- `TestTransitionFromEnded/GitCommit_with_files_condenses` (line 242)\n- `TestTransitionFromEnded/GitCommit_without_files_discards` (line 249)\n- `TestTransitionBackwardCompat/empty_phase_GitCommit_treated_as_IDLE` (line 298)\n- `TestApplyTransition_CallsHandlerForCondense` (line 444) — update actions list\n- `TestApplyTransition_CallsHandlerForCondenseIfFilesTouched` (line 462) — update actions list\n- `TestApplyTransition_CallsHandlerForDiscardIfNoFiles` (line 478) — update actions list\n- `TestApplyTransition_ReturnsHandlerError_ButRunsCommonActions` (lines 528, 537-538) — update actions list AND remove the LastInteractionTime assertion (no common action to test here anymore)\n\n### 3. `cmd/entire/cli/session/phase_test.go` — Update Mermaid diagram test\n\n`TestTransitionDiagram_ContainsAllStates` (line ~380) — the generated diagram text may change since GitCommit transitions no longer include UpdateLastInteraction.\n\n## Verification\n\n```bash\nmise run fmt && mise run lint && mise run test:ci\n```\n\n\nIf you need specific details from before exiting plan mode (like exact code snippets, error messages, or content you generated), read the full transcript at: /Users/soph/.claude/projects/-Users-soph-Work-entire-devenv-cli/8ae52333-e3d1-4dcd-81c9-c6bc81ec8814.jsonl"